_:Nab3ae10b9ef14e149f9cbd4c6c649910 <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Michael Tomlinson was Minister of State at the Home Office between 7 December 2023 and 5 July 2024.</p>\n\n<p>He was Solicitor General between 7 September 2022 and 7 December 2023.</p>\n\n<p>He was previously a Vice Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) between 8 July 2022 and 7 September 2022, and Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) between 14 February 2020 and 8 July 2022.</p>\n" <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
