<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/michael-tomlinson> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Michael Tomlinson was Minister of State at the Home Office between 7 December 2023 and 5 July 2024. He was Solicitor General between 7 September 2022 and 7 December 2023. He was previously a Vice Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) between 8 July 2022 and 7 September 2022, and Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) between 14 February 2020 and 8 July 2022."@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
